                                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Why Everyone Hates the World's Most Famous Font]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/comic-sans-ms-everyone-hates-worlds-most-famous-font/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Tony Phillips]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/comic-style-illustration-with-the-words-comic-sans-in-a-speech-bubble-surrounded-by-bursts-asking-hate-and-love.png" length="1026" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Microsoft]]></category><category><![CDATA[Microsoft Office]]></category><category><![CDATA[Microsoft Word]]></category><category><![CDATA[Microsoft PowerPoint]]></category><category><![CDATA[Microsoft Excel]]></category><category><![CDATA[Microsoft Outlook]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Does this typeface really deserve the hate it gets?
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>For decades, even some of the most mildly mannered people have become enraged at the sight of the unassuming, cheery typeface that is Comic Sans. Whether used on birthday cards, posters, wedding invitations, or road signs, it's guaranteed to spark debate.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 24 Sep 2025 15:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/comic-sans-ms-everyone-hates-worlds-most-famous-font/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Top Tech Deals: Steam Deck, Roku Mini LED TV, Anker Chargers, and More!]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/weekly-tech-deals-steam-deck-roku-mini-led-tv-anker-chargers-and-more/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Cory Gunther]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/copy-of-tri-fold-1920px-header-2.jpg" length="850" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Deals]]></category><category><![CDATA[Steam Deck]]></category><category><![CDATA[Roku]]></category><category><![CDATA[Anker]]></category><description><![CDATA[
